t: "They will all appear before Allah, and the lowly ňĻfollowersňļ will appeal to the arrogant ňĻleadersňļ, ‚ÄúWe were your ňĻdedicatedňļ followers, so will you ňĻthenňļ protect us from Allah‚Äôs torment in any way?‚ÄĚ They will reply, ‚ÄúHad Allah guided us, we would have guided you. ňĻNowňļ it is all the same for us whether we suffer patiently or impatiently, there is no escape for us.‚ÄĚ"